title: SF1 SJ1.5: Two new budget smartphones in town
text:
Sep 22, 2015, 07.47 AM | Source: CNBC-TV18 SF1 & SJ1.5: Two new budget smartphones in town Obi Worldphone’s two sub-USD 200 smartphones pack a punch when given their spec-sheet for the price they are being offered at. Launched in San Francisco and backed by former CEO of Apple, John Sculley, these new smartphones are sure to grab the attentions of the market.
